1220年出生在苏格兰培爾阿爾时，她的父亲Sir David de Hastings VII Earl of Atholl30岁，母亲Forbhlaith Countess of Atholl25岁。她于1239年与John de Strathbogie Earl Of Atholl在苏格兰培爾阿爾结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。她去世于1264年12月25日之前在她的家乡。"},"hr":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"oko 1220.–prije 25. prosinca 1264.","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245.–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247.","1196–1244":"1196–1244.","before 1242":"prije 1242.","before 25 December 1266":"prije 25. prosinca 1264.","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239.","1247":"1247.","1245":"1245.","1244":"1244.","about 1220":"oko 1220.","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Škotska, United Kingdom","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"okolo 1220–před 25. prosince 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"před 1242","before 25 December 1266":"před 25. prosince 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"okolo 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Skotsko, United Kingdom","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Skotsko, United Kingdom"},"da":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"omkring 1220–før 25. december 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"før 1242","before 25 December 1266":"før 25. december 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"omkring 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Skotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Skotland","Scotland":"Skotland, United Kingdom","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Skotland, United Kingdom"},"nl":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"circa 1220–vóór 25 december 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"vóór 1242","before 25 December 1266":"vóór 25 december 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"circa 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Schotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Schotland","Scotland":"Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk"},"en":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"about 1220–before 25 December 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"before 1242","before 25 December 1266":"before 25 December 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"about 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland, United Kingdom","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Scotland, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Hastings","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English and Scottish: habitational name from Hastings (Sussex), near which the English army was defeated by the Normans in 1066. The placename derives from an Old English personal name <i>Hǣsta</i> + the Old English groupname suffix <i>-ingas</i>. In the latter part of the 12th century, at the time of William the Lion, the surname was taken to Scotland, where it assimilated instances of the native Scottish surname <b>Harestane</b>.","English: variant of   Hasting   with Middle English genitival <i>-s</i>.","Irish: Anglicized form of Gaelic <b>Ó hOistín</b> ‘descendant of <i>Oistín</i>’, the Gaelic form of the personal name <i>Augustine</i> (see   Austin  )."],"variants":[{"name":"Hasting","meanings":["English: from the Norman personal name <i>Hastang</i>, <i>Hastenc</i>, <i>Hasten</i> (Old Norse <i>Hásteinn</i> ‘high’ + ‘stone’). See also   Hastings  ."]},{"name":"Heston","meanings":["English: habitational name from Heston (Middlesex) or Histon (Cambridgeshire). The Middlesex placename derives from Old English <i>hǣs</i> ‘brushwood’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, estate’, while the Cambridgeshire placename may derive from Old English <i>hyse</i> ‘shoot, tendril’, also ‘son, youth’, + <i>tūn</i>.","Irish (Mayo): variant of   Hastings  ."]}]},{"name":"Ada","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Of uncertain origin; it was not in general use before the late 18th century. It may be a Latinate variant of the biblical name   Adah .  However, it has also been explained as a pet form of   Adele   and   Adelaide  , Germanic female names of which the first element is <i>adal</i> ‘noble’. It was borne by a 7th-century abbess of Saint-Julien-des-Prés at Le Mans."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Ada Hastings was born about 1220, in Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland, her father, Sir David de Hastings VII Earl of Atholl, was 30 and her mother, Forbhlaith Countess of Atholl, was 25. She married John de Strathbogie Earl Of Atholl in 1239, in Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died before 25 December 1264, in her hometown."},"et":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"umbes 1220–enne 25. detsembrit 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"enne 1242","before 25 December 1266":"enne 25. detsembrit 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"umbes 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"noin 1220–ennen vuotta 25. joulukuuta 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"ennen vuotta 1242","before 25 December 1266":"ennen vuotta 25. joulukuuta 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"noin 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Atholl, Perth & Kinross, Scotland":"Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Strathbogie Castle, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Huntly, Aberdeenshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1220–before 25 December 1266":"environ 1220–avant 25 décembre 1264","1220–1264":"1220–1264","1218–1264":"1218–1264","1245–1270":"1245–1270","1192–1247":"1192–1247","1196–1244":"1196–1244","before 1242":"avant 1242","before 25 December 1266":"avant 25 décembre 1264","1264":"1264","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1270":"1270","1192":"1192","1239":"1239","1247":"1247","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","about 1220":"environ 1220","1218":"1218","Atholl, Perthshire, Scotland":"Atholl, Pert